a register dump, and if <br />you do that multiple times you can look at the EIP values and try to get <br />a feel for where it's looping.<br /><br />Of course, if it's looping with interrupts disabled, even this won't <br />work, but it's worth checking out.<br /><br />		Linus<br /><br /><br /></pre><div align="center"><div class="shariff" data-services="[&quot;reddit&quot;]" data-theme="grey" data-lang="en" data-backend-url="//shariff.lkml.org/index.php"></div></div></td><td width="32" rowspan="2" class="c" valign="top"><img src="/images/icornerr.gif" width="32" height="32" alt="\" /></td></tr><tr><td align="right" valign="bottom">
